
'''''De Voortrekkers''''' ni film idafite amajwi yasohotse 1916 yamenyakanye nka filime ya mbere muri   [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] . <ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/268360352_A_tale_of_two_nations_South_Africa_De_Voortrekkers_and_Come_See_the_Bioscope</ref> Yakozwe na African Film Productions kandi iyobowe na Harold M<ref>https://www.africa-in-motion.org.uk/resources/africas-lost-classics/exhibition/event/315/</ref>. Shaw, yerekana " Great Trek " ya Boers yo mu myaka ya za 1830, isozwa n’imyidagaduro ya hegemonike y’Intambara y’amaraso yabaye ku ya 16 Ukuboza 1838, igihe Abanyafurika bitwaje intwaro<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/m0j46rnm?hl=nl</ref> . yatsinze ibihumbi byinshi Zulus . ''Abakomoka kuri voortrekkers'' bavuga ururimi rw’Ubuholandi cyangwa "abapayiniya" bitabiriye Great Trek bubahaga filime kandi barayikoresha mu kwibuka ibirori<ref>https://www.taylorfrancis.com/chapters/colonizing-nation-de-voortrekkers-1916-jacqueline-maingard/10.4324/9780203354513-6</ref>, bikaba bigize igice cy’amakimbirane menshi mu mateka ya [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>http://africultures.com/films/?no=12272</ref>. Abanyafurika babigaragaje mu byumba by’ishuri imyaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo kandi barabigaragaza buri mwaka mu birori mbonezamubano bizihiza isabukuru y'intambara<ref>https://context.reverso.net/translation/dutch-english/De+voortrekkers+zijn</ref>.<ref>https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/'De-Voortrekkers'-(1916)%3A-Some-Stereotypes-and-Zyl/319d3dfcec2aeb12264c0d1afd18985670ed9c6a</ref>

''De Voortrekkers'' yerekanwe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo ahitwa Krugersdorp ku ya 14 Ukuboza 1916, hasigaye iminsi ibiri ngo isabukuru y'imyaka 78 imaze ibaye<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=182343.html</ref>. Nyuma yaje gukwirakwizwa mu magambo ahinnye muri sinema zo mu [[Bwongereza]], [[Amerika]], [[Kanada]], n'ahandi hanze ya Afurika ku izina rya ''Winning a Continent''<ref>https://www.unisa.ac.za/sites/corporate/default/About/Leading-change/Articles/Reimaging-identity-through-film-music-in-De-Voortrekkers</ref> .  Intertitles zikoreshwa muri firime y'umwimerere no mubisohoka nyuma ikoresha imiterere ya ecran yerekana inyandiko mucyongereza no muri [[Ikinyafurikansi|Afrikaans]] . <ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j8M5vkqvfug "De Voortrekkers (1916) with new orchestral score"], 19:52 segment of film with added music, uploaded by Chris Jeffrey on 23 February 2017 onto [[YouTube]] (San Bruno, California, United States). Retrieved 12 August 2021.</ref>

